messages.text: know how we opened grandpa tims time capsule today?
well he had a letter addressed to me..
no.. i was a baby when he died..
and he left a time capsule??
ya, something for our family to open 20 years after his death
have u showed anyone the letter? Mayb they know wat it means.
grandpa tim did? or u think so?
u know how he died right??
n his sleep. natural causes i hear.
nothin, im jus sayin.. how can a rather healthy man jus all the sudden die..
in his sleep without a reason…
but really, wat r u sayin??
mom always thought he was..well, killed..
do u kno how u sound right now!?
wats 2 think about?! that notion is insane!!
rich man, a lot of wealth..
John was an unruly child anyway..
never amounted 2 anything, his father, grandpa tim, never gave him anything..
oldest son, knows that if he dies, he gets the cut..
in grandpa tims own handwriting, in his will, he said John was 2 get the money if he passed
he was a failure but he is the oldest.
and u know, everyone said grandpa tim played favs.
but he loved my mom, not John.
then y would he send me a letter sayin this..
he wants to warn me of John..
ur accusing grandpa tims oldest son, ur and my uncle, of killing his father
greed can take ahold of any man..
then tell me y he wrote this message??
he knew i wouldnt get it until now..
was 2 young 2 know anything.. now im old enough 2 know..
so ur sayin he could predict the future??
well if he put that n the time capsule, then he would have had to of known he was goin 2 be killed
ok, ur way over thinkin it..
expose John for the fraud he is..
but none of his kids were close to him..
no one knew where the money would go!
mom and dad talk about it all the time..
idk, John seemed hesitant bout opening this thing n the first place..
whateves Mary. this is jus bogus.
shit, everyone is asking me wat i got..
he wasnt close 2 any of them, of course he thought that!!
jus dont have a good feelin..
im gonna check on her, see wat she thinks..
a bit insensitive dont u think..
asked her wat this letter meant.
hasnt given me a straight answer..
he knew wat they were goin 2 do..
John did kill him.. smothered him..
she was supposed to get a cut..
so that was the fallin out?!
